OL,3,CCash-strapped council plans to axe
OL,4,Clollipop ladies and men
OL,6,FThe plans have faced criticism from
OL,7,Fparents - with one angry mother from
OL,8,FBridge Farm Primary School in
OL,9,FWhitchurch describing the idea as
OL,10,F"absolute insanity."
OL,12,FShe said: "We have three lollipop
OL,13,Fladies at our school, and this would
OL,14,Fbe a huge loss.
OL,16,F"It is an absolutely shameful move by
OL,17,Fthe council. These people's roles are
OL,18,Fso important to ensuring the safety of
OL,19,Fchildren - they're literally
OL,20,Fcontracted to work five hours per week.
