OL,6,F"I'm honestly fuming about it, not
OL,7,Fleast because our lollipop lady is the
OL,8,Floveliest lady you'll ever meet.
OL,10,F"She knows absolutely everyone's
OL,11,Fnames, buys the kids little toys for
OL,12,FHalloween and is just lush, she's been
OL,13,Fdoing it for nearly 20 years."
OL,15,FGreen council leader Cllr Tony Dyer
OL,16,Fsaid it would face bankruptcy if it
OL,17,Fcould not close the financial gap so
